high_descs: Turn right and begin walking across the room, then turn right and walk up to the small black shelving unit in between the counter and the trash bag.
Pick up the red sweet potato that is on top of the black shelving unit.
Turn right and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Wash the red sweet potato in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the white table, then turn right to face the black shelving unit.
Pace the clean red sweet potato on top of the black shelving unit to the right of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sweet potato on top of a black shelving unit.

high_descs: Turn right and move to the table next to the oven then turn right and face the small table next to the trash bag on the floor.
Pick up the peach to the right of the fork from the table.
Turn right, move forward past the kitchen counter, then turn left at the sink.
Place the peach in the sink in the corner closest to you then turn on the water to wash it.
Pick up the peach from the sink, turn around, move towards the table with the toaster on it, then turn around and face the small table next to the trash bag.
Place the peach to the right of the sponge on the corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed peach on a table.

high_descs: Turn right, head towards the white table, and then turn left to face the black table.
Pick up the plum beside the bread on the table.
Turn right and head towards the sink on your left.
Place the plum in the sink, rinse it, and pick it back up.
Turn left and head towards the black table on your left.
Place the plum to the right of the green sponge on the table.
anns.task_desc: Wash the plum from the black table.
